---
import img1 from "../assets/horse16.jpg";
import img2 from "../assets/horse.jpg";
import img3 from "../assets/P1010419.jpg";

import img5 from "../assets/website_announcement.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Fallen Oaks Equine Rescue | About">
  <div
    class="bg-[#fefce8] min-h-[calc(100vh-10rem)] px-4 lg:px-0 flex flex-col items-center"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-full lg:w-2/5 pt-32 pb-8 lg:pb-16 gap-y-12 sm:gap-y-24"
    >
      <div style="transform: scale(0); animation: jump 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0.01, 0.25, 1) 0.2s forwards;" class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide">About us</div>
      <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center sm:max-h-40 w-full lg:w-1/3">
        <Image
          src={img1}
          alt=""
          style="filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 5px #000); transform: scale(0); animation: jump-rotate-1 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0.01, 0.25, 1) 0.6s forwards;"
          class="max-h-64 w-auto sm:max-h-auto sm:h-64 lg:max-w-lg mx-auto z-0 rounded-lg -rotate-3 bg-neutral-400 border-white border-8"
        />
        <Image
          src={img2}
          alt=""
          style="filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 5px #000); transform: scale(0); animation: jump-rotate-2 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0.01, 0.25, 1) 0.8s forwards;"
          class="hidden sm:block h-64 max-w-lg mx-auto z-0 rounded-lg rotate-3 bg-neutral-400 border-white border-8"
        />
        <Image
          src={img3}
          alt=""
          style="filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 5px #000); transform: scale(0); animation: jump-rotate-1 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0.01, 0.25, 1) 1.0s forwards;"
          class="hidden sm:block h-64 max-w-lg mx-auto z-0 rounded-lg -rotate-3 bg-neutral-400 border-white border-8"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="text-base lg:text-xl" style="transform: scale(0); animation: jump 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0.01, 0.25, 1) 1.2s forwards;">
        <p>
          Fallen Oak Equine Rescue and Rehabilitation, Inc. is located on 7 acres in beautiful Belleview, Florida. We currently operate out of a 5 stall barn, pasture for grazing, and a round pen for training and evaluating rescued horses. We rely on our devoted foster homes to help us transition horses from our facility to their forever home, and to help us when numbers of horses in-need force us to overflow. We could not do what we do without our team of foster parents!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="border-neutral-400 border-1 w-full lg:w-2/3 pb-8 lg:pb-16" 
    style="opacity: 0; animation: fadein 0.5s ease 1.6s forwards;"/>
    <div 
    style="opacity: 0; animation: fadein 0.5s ease 1.8s forwards;" class="w-full lg:w-2/3 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start justify-center pb-16 gap-y-8 lg:gap-y-16">
      <div class="lg:border-r-2 lg:border-neutral-400 gap-y-8 w-full lg:w-1/3 lg:pr-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-between" id="mission">
          <div class="text-3xl text-center uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide">
            Our mission
          </div>
          <Image src={img1} alt="" class="h-48 w-48 rounded-lg -rotate-3 bg-neutral-400 border-white border-8" 
          style="filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 5px #000)" />
          <div class="text-base lg:text-sm">
            <p>
              Our goal is to rescue, rehabilitate and rehome abused and neglected horses. We provide sanctuary to horses that are unadoptable or require special care.
            </p>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:border-r-2 lg:border-neutral-400 gap-y-8 w-full lg:w-1/3 lg:ml-4 lg:pr-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-between" id="history">
          <div class="text-3xl text-center uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide">
            Our history
          </div>
          <Image src={img2} alt="" class="h-48 w-48 rounded-lg rotate-3 bg-neutral-400 border-white border-8" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 5px #000)" />
          <div  class="text-base lg:text-sm">
            <p>
              Fallen Oak was established in December 2012 in Central Florida. Kim Sweeney is the 3rd president of Fallen Oak as of Feb 1st 2020. Kim has cared for and rehabilitated over 160 horses as of May 2024.
            </p>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="gap-y-8 w-full lg:w-1/3 lg:ml-4 lg:pr-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-between" id="mascot">

          <div class="text-3xl text-center  uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide">
            Our mascot
          </div>
          <Image src={img5} alt="" class="w-72 rounded-lg -rotate-3 bg-neutral-400 border-white border-8" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 5px #000)"/>
          <div class="text-base lg:text-sm">
            <p>
              Our mascot, <span class="font-semibold">Fallen Oakley</span>, was designed around our first rescue horse Early Bird! Early Bird was a Paint and that is what inspired Fallen Oakleys blue spots. Her cutiemark is an Oak tree with 2 equines underneath, representing the care and hospitality she provides to all the horses under her care.
            </p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>